QuestData.Title: Return to Oribos
QuestData.Description:
I wish you could stay and relax here, maybe enjoy a play at the Star Lake Amphitheater, but there's simply no time!
There are other realms out there that need your help, too.
You will always be a friend of the Court, but I'm afraid you must return to Oribos. The Shadowlands needs you!
QuestData.RewardText: Your efforts in Ardenweald have not gone unnoticed, Maw Walker.
